Big Brother Naija housemate, Kiddwaya, has spoken on the disqualification of his love interest, Erica. He said “I hope she gets the strength to count her blessings. Kiddwaya during a conversation with Vee, Laycon and Trickytee, said he is hurt by Erica’s disqualification. He said, “Erica losing all the money she worked for really hurts. He said “I hope she gets the strength to count her blessings. “What pains me is the money you lose when disqualified. I think she has 1.8 million and it’s all gone.” Erica was disqualified on Sunday for breaking different house rules.